          "name": "Weapon Mounts",
          "subtype": "ability",
          "text": "This vehicle has four weapon mounts, one on each corner of the gondola. At purchase, these weapon mounts are initially empty. Installing or uninstalling a weapon into a mount requires 3 hours, a successful DC 35 Crafting check, and an appropriate weapon. Three of these weapon mounts can be equipped with Medium or smaller ranged siege weapons, and the fourth can be equipped with a Large or smaller ranged siege weapon.",
